translate schinese chapter13_f6a7e59d:

    # Aa "I’m sorry. I shouldn’t have brought it up."
    Aa "抱歉。我不应该提起这件事的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1255
translate schinese chapter13_a425f53a:

    # cyr "Don’t be. I want to talk about them.{w} I’m trying to be as open as I can about everything that’s happened, ya know?"
    cyr "没事。我想要聊聊他们。{w}我正试着尽力接受正发生的一切。"

# game/b13.rpy:1257
translate schinese chapter13_05419c9b:

    # Aa "In that case, why don’t you tell me about them?"
    Aa "那，为什么不告诉我关于他们的事呢？"

# game/b13.rpy:1258
translate schinese chapter13_12b0057b:

    # cyr "Boy... Where do I even begin?"
    cyr "好家伙...这要我从何谈起呢？"

# game/b13.rpy:1260
translate schinese chapter13_aaba36bc:

    # Aa "Why not a rousing game of 20 questions?"
    Aa "为什么不来场令人激动的20问游戏呢？"

# game/b13.rpy:1261
translate schinese chapter13_9c154b39:

    # cyr "Ha. I think I’ll take you up on that."
    cyr "哈。我想我会完胜你的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1263
translate schinese chapter13_85282795:

    # "Aaron and I get comfortable around the dying campfire."
    "坐在干燥的篝火旁边，Aaron和我都感到无比舒适。"

# game/b13.rpy:1264
translate schinese chapter13_5c105ff6:

    # "For the next hour or so, he asks me about random facts of my previous life."
    "接下来的一个小时左右，他随意问了些我过去生活的事情。"

# game/b13.rpy:1266
translate schinese chapter13_665cd8c2:

    # "He eventually takes his Axiom out to start typing in it, saying he’s been researching how the old world used to be."
    "他最终拿出Axiom并开始输入我刚才所说的内容，他说他一直在研究旧世界过去的样子。"

# game/b13.rpy:1267
translate schinese chapter13_dea4e8d0:

    # "Aaron is quite attentive throughout my many ramblings."
    "Aaron在我漫无边际的谈话中非常专注。"

# game/b13.rpy:1268
translate schinese chapter13_e7b17c85:

    # "He’s picking up on things I wouldn’t consider abnormal, but are wildly different than how he grew up."
    "他正在研究一些我认为很寻常，但在他成长过程中迥然不同的事情。"

# game/b13.rpy:1270
translate schinese chapter13_f5054a1c:

    # Aa "Your parents sound wonderful, Cyrus. I can only imagine how hard it must have been to go through school like that."
    Aa "你的父母听起来很棒，Cyrus。我能想象你完成学业的过程有多困难。"

# game/b13.rpy:1271
translate schinese chapter13_c539fe61:

    # cyr "It wasn’t the worst. I had a lot of help along the way. Definitely couldn’t have done it without them."
    cyr "还没有糟糕到哪去。一路上我受到了很多帮助，如果没有他们我根本走不下去。"

# game/b13.rpy:1273
translate schinese chapter13_6c87fa1d:

    # Aa "A proper support system is all you need."
    Aa "啊，一路上的帮助确实能让人宽心不少。"

# game/b13.rpy:1275
translate schinese chapter13_bf8f05ef:

    # "Aaron shuts off his Axiom before he leans back."
    "Aaron关闭了Axiom，身体稍稍后仰。"

# game/b13.rpy:1277
translate schinese chapter13_74420e6a:

    # Aa "I hope your old way of life becomes more commonplace in the future."
    Aa "我希望你的旧世界生活方式能在未来变得稀松平常。"

# game/b13.rpy:1278
translate schinese chapter13_df06a858:

    # cyr "It wasn’t all sunshine and rainbows.{w} The world was still pretty shitty back in the day; just a different shade of shitty."
    cyr "过去的世界也不尽是美好。{w}它也有很糟糕的地方，只是和如今不同罢了。"
#*幸福千遍一律，灾难各有千秋
# game/b13.rpy:1280
translate schinese chapter13_915cbf18:

    # Aa "Things seemed a lot more simple back then."
    Aa "那时的事情看起来简单多了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1281
translate schinese chapter13_1c799bc5:

    # cyr "That’s probably because I can’t properly explain how complicated it all was."
    cyr "那可能是因为我没办法解释它有多复杂。"

# game/b13.rpy:1282
translate schinese chapter13_ccdf648d:

    # cyr "The government was pretty shitty most of the time, and healthcare was way too expensive."
    cyr "大多数时候，政府就像坨屎，而且医保太贵了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1283
translate schinese chapter13_2a7f868b:

    # cyr "My folks weren’t super well-off for most of my life. We made do, but it was rough."
    cyr "我的家人手头经常不是很宽裕。虽然我们还是跌跌撞撞地挺了过去，但是过程的确艰难。"

# game/b13.rpy:1284
translate schinese chapter13_2566f886:

    # cyr "Part of the reason I went to work for Current was to help my paretns pay for my college expenses."
    cyr "我去Current实习的一部分原因就是为了帮父母付我的大学学费。"

# game/b13.rpy:1286
translate schinese chapter13_9f6e953a:

    # Aa "That’s very admirable of you, Cyrus. I’m sure they’re proud of you."
    Aa "令人倾佩，Cyrus。我很确定他们以你为傲。"

# game/b13.rpy:1287
translate schinese chapter13_bb1b2cca:

    # cyr "I’d like to think so. They did a good job raising me.{w} I miss them a lot, to be honest."
    cyr "但愿如此吧。他们真的是很好的父母。{w}说真的，我很想他们。"

# game/b13.rpy:1288
translate schinese chapter13_d63d3b03:

    # Aa "I can imagine."
    Aa "我能体会到。"

# game/b13.rpy:1289
translate schinese chapter13_d26c1d67:

    # "Aaron sits straight to face me."
    "Aaron笔直的坐着，面对着我。"

# game/b13.rpy:1291
translate schinese chapter13_72eda3ae:

    # Aa "Well, it’s not very fair of me to ask about your past without telling you about mine."
    Aa "好吧，只询问你的过去却不讲讲我自己的有点不太公平。"

# game/b13.rpy:1292
translate schinese chapter13_d1247f0f:

    # cyr "What?{w=0.3} You wanna tell me about how you grew up?"
    cyr "什么？{w=0.3}你想要告诉我你是如何长大的吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:1293
translate schinese chapter13_800119e1:

    # Aa "Sure, as you know I have a lot of stories."
    Aa "当然，你知道的我有很多故事。"

# game/b13.rpy:1294
translate schinese chapter13_42fba13e:

    # cyr "I’m all ears. I’ve been curious about a few things, to be honest."
    cyr "洗耳恭听。说实话，我对一些东西还是很好奇的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1296
translate schinese chapter13_f846b770:

    # Aa "Oh yeah? Like what?"
    Aa "哦？是吗？比如？"

# game/b13.rpy:1297
translate schinese chapter13_562c748e:

    # cyr "I’m curious how you met everyone. You told me you met Lance and Reggie at the orphanage. What was it like growing up?"
    cyr "我很好奇你是怎么认识大家的。你说你在孤儿院认识了Lance和Reggie。那里的生活怎么样？"

# game/b13.rpy:1299
translate schinese chapter13_73454845:

    # Aa "Ah... The orphanage. Obviously it wasn’t an ideal situation to be in, but we made it work the best we could."
    Aa "额...孤儿院。显然，那里的环境不是很理想，但我们都尽力让它变得更好。"

# game/b13.rpy:1300
translate schinese chapter13_b2491096:

    # Aa "Despite how strict the staff were, they tried to make sure we were well-fed and comfortable.{w} It was a poor establishment, however, so we didn’t have many luxuries."
    Aa "尽管那里的员工很严格，但他们努力地确保让我们吃饱，过得舒适。{w}孤儿院很穷，所以我们没有太多奢侈品。"

# game/b13.rpy:1302
translate schinese chapter13_4896ae2a:

    # Aa "Lance, Reggie, and I shared a small room together. I had a bit of a growth spurt when I was young.{w} I remember having to sleep on the floor for a little while until they replaced my bed."
    Aa "Lance，Reggie和我一起住在一个很小的房间里。我还小的时候，个头猛窜。{w}我还记得在他们给我换了床之前，我不得不睡在地上的情景。"

# game/b13.rpy:1303
translate schinese chapter13_f6192027:

    # Aa "Every now and then, I try to anonymously donate plumes to help out."
    Aa "我现在还时不时地给孤儿院匿名捐赠。"

# game/b13.rpy:1304
translate schinese chapter13_cd27f680:

    # "I nod along as Aaron recollects his childhood, not wanting to interrupt."
    "Aaron回忆起他的童年时，我点了点头，不想打断他。"

# game/b13.rpy:1305
translate schinese chapter13_9f8a4c82:

    # Aa "When Reggie turned 18, he got accepted for a scholarship and was able to travel to go to school. We only saw him a few times a year after that."
    Aa "当Reggie 18岁时，他获得了奖学金被学校录取，能够走读上学。在那之后，一年内我们只能见到他几次了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1306
translate schinese chapter13_5fded71a:

    # "Aaron’s voice starts getting a little somber."
    "Aaron的声音开始变得有些低沉。"

# game/b13.rpy:1308
translate schinese chapter13_86e7e0a4:

    # Aa "It was just me and Lance in that little room for a while. I think I was about 14 at the time. We played and talked a lot, but it was still lonely."
    Aa "只剩下我和Lance在那小小的房间里呆了一段时间。我想那时我才14。虽然我们经常在一起玩耍，交谈，但仍然觉得很孤独。"

# game/b13.rpy:1309
translate schinese chapter13_04f28f8f:

    # Aa "At the time, it wasn’t very common for kids to get adopted. Those who did usually showed some sort of promise.{w} Basically if you weren’t useful in some way shape or form, you didn’t get to leave."
    Aa "那时，领养孩子并不常见。被领养的孩子通常需要做出一些保证。{w}如果你在某些方面没用的话，你不可能被收养。"

# game/b13.rpy:1311
translate schinese chapter13_42fafe24:

    # Aa "Reggie actually got asked a few times, but said he’d only go if we were able to go with him.{w} In the end, it never worked out."
    Aa "实际上Reggie收到了好几次领养申请，但他说除非我们和他一起被领养，否则他就不答应。{w}而直到最后他还是没能被领养。"

# game/b13.rpy:1313
translate schinese chapter13_1d142e21:

    # Aa "Then... I turned 18. I was finally old enough to work.{w} A nearby factory had a stranglehold on the orphanage. They exploited the small staff of the orphanage to get free laborers."
    Aa "然后...我终于18岁。能去工作了。{w}附近的一家工厂控制了孤儿院。他们要征用孤儿充当免费的劳动力。"

# game/b13.rpy:1314
translate schinese chapter13_0ea53df4:

    # Aa "I didn’t want to cause a fuss, so I decided to go willingly."
    Aa "我不想引起麻烦，所以我自愿去了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1316
translate schinese chapter13_cd8833b1:

    # Aa "I remember how teary eyed everyone was, especially Lance.{w} Lance wasn’t of age yet, but he wouldn’t let me leave alone, and insisted I come with him."
    Aa "我记得每个人的眼睛都泪汪汪的，尤其是Lance。{w}Lance还未成年，但他坚持要我带他一起去。"

# game/b13.rpy:1317
translate schinese chapter13_1bb32ef9:

    # "Aaron manages to chuckle while reminiscing."
    "Aaron在回忆时咯咯地笑了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1319
translate schinese chapter13_de9d37ef:

    # Aa "He was a needy guy, I’ll tell you what. Always needed reassurance."
    Aa "要我说，他是一个需要关心的人。总是需要宽慰。"

# game/b13.rpy:1321
translate schinese chapter13_f1c2c9a5:

    # Aa "Reggie graduated from intermediate level of education and was on his way to university, but after hearing about us leaving, he decided to drop it all and come back to us."
    Aa "当时Reggie中学毕业，正在去大学的路上，但在听到我们离开的消息后，他决定放弃这一切，回到我们身边。"

# game/b13.rpy:1322
translate schinese chapter13_19b13948:

    # Aa "Factory life, well... It didn’t work out for me, to say the least.{w} They didn’t pay us much and would often delay paying us all together."
    Aa "工厂的生活，好吧...至少对我来说不行。{w}他们给我们的工资不多，而且还经常拖欠。"

# game/b13.rpy:1323
translate schinese chapter13_44647e4e:

    # Aa "They kept pushing us to work. Often times it led to more... violent outcomes."
    Aa "他们强迫我们工作。这通常会导致更多...暴力的结果。"

# game/b13.rpy:1325
translate schinese chapter13_ed32b729:

    # Aa "I still remember the time they threw a wrench at Lance’s face, and the beating I gave the supervisor who did it."
    Aa "我仍然记得有一次他们朝Lance脸上扔扳手，然后我打了一顿做这件事的主管。"

# game/b13.rpy:1326
translate schinese chapter13_4af28b62:

    # Aa "After a few months, I got the courage to get us all to run away. We ran away as fast and as far as we could."
    Aa "在几个月后，我鼓起勇气让大家一起逃跑。我们飞快的跑啊，跑得越远越好。"

# game/b13.rpy:1328
translate schinese chapter13_ad8ccfeb:

    # Aa "I was bitter, very bitter.{w} My folks abandoned me, I couldn’t find a job, and I barely knew anything."
    Aa "我那时很难受，非常的痛苦。{w}我的家人背叛了我，我找不到工作，而且我对外面的世界几乎一无所知。"

# game/b13.rpy:1329
translate schinese chapter13_a8c2b764:

    # Aa "I had to take that anger out on something."
    Aa "我不得不在某些事情上发泄。"

# game/b13.rpy:1333
translate schinese chapter13_d36bdc70:

    # Aa "..."
    Aa "..."

# game/b13.rpy:1334
translate schinese chapter13_b2812a36:

    # cyr "Hey, what’s wrong?"
    cyr "嘿，怎么了？"

# game/b13.rpy:1336
translate schinese chapter13_3204bb9a:

    # Aa "Cyrus.{cps=3}..{/cps}{w=0.4} I did a lot of awful things. Things I’m ashamed to admit.{w} I was angry at the world around me, and hurt a lot of people."
    Aa "Cyrus.{cps=3}..{/cps}{w=0.4}我做了很多错事。有很多我愧于承认的事情。我对周围的世界感到愤怒，并且伤害了很多人。"

# game/b13.rpy:1345
translate schinese chapter13_27837876:
#*清风/炽镜-Aaron的回忆
    # Aa "At first, I made it a point to not attack anyone for no reason, so we only targeted rival gangs."
    Aa "一开始，我们坚守着绝不无缘无故攻击别人的原则，我们只会对敌对帮派出手。"

# game/b13.rpy:1346
translate schinese chapter13_0719f0b4:

    # Aa "That 'code of honor' didn’t last long though."
    Aa "不过这条『荣誉守则』没有持续多久。"

# game/b13.rpy:1371
translate schinese chapter13_5aa52e61:

    # Aa "We’d raid any camps we came across in the desert. There was a lot of bloodshed."
    Aa "我们会袭击在荒漠中遇到的任何营地。那时打打杀杀算是家常便饭。"

# game/b13.rpy:1372
translate schinese chapter13_69cbf436:

    # Aa "Even now, I can clearly hear the sound of a bat smacking against a sleeping man’s skull. It was efficient and easy."
    Aa "即使来到现在，我耳边仍能清晰地听到球棒被抡圆后砸向熟睡的受害者头颅的那种闷响。这么做轻松又省事儿。"

# game/b13.rpy:1382
translate schinese chapter13_34fc0d28:

    # Aa "It felt good to get all of my anger out on somebody, anybody.{w} We worked as a team for a while, but I knew deep down I just wanted to raise hell."
    Aa "把我全身的怒火发泄到某人，也许是任何人身上，这种感觉很不错。{w}我们作为一个小团队肆虐了一段时间，我只想要大闹一番。"

# game/b13.rpy:1383
translate schinese chapter13_8b6d29f7:

    # Aa "Eventually our small band of three grew bigger and bigger. We’d take in people over time that suited our interest, eventually becoming a respectable desert gang."
    Aa "我们三个人的小团伙发展得越来越壮大。随着时间流逝，我们会接纳志同道合的人入伙，最终成了某片荒漠震慑一方的帮派。"

# game/b13.rpy:1402
translate schinese chapter13_a613f73f:

    # Aa "That’s actually how we ended up meeting Karin. We ran into her during one of our raids.{w} Apparently we had our eyes set on the same target."
    Aa "实际上我们就是这样结识Karin的。我们在一次袭击中撞见了她。{w}显而易见，我们都盯上了同一个目标。"

# game/b13.rpy:1403
translate schinese chapter13_b7e8f668:

    # Aa "It turned into a competition, more or less, to see who could do the most damage."
    Aa "或多或少，这次行动变成了一场竞赛，我们想比试下哪一方造成的伤害最严重。"

# game/b13.rpy:1404
translate schinese chapter13_b892184e:

    # Aa "After everything went down, everyone was pretty much spent for the night.{w} In the end, there was no clear winner."
    Aa "等到硝烟落尽，每个人因为整晚的战斗差不多都耗尽了最后一丝气力。{w}这场比赛最后没有等来赢家。"

# game/b13.rpy:1405
translate schinese chapter13_1b24d197:

    # Aa "But she stuck around after that and we eventually merged our gangs together...{w} I can’t deny that it was an exhilarating time in my life."
    Aa "不过在这之后她没有离开，最终我们合并了彼此的小队...{w}不可否认，那是我这辈子里一段振奋人心的时光。"

# game/b13.rpy:1415
translate schinese chapter13_6c07c606:

    # "Aaron sighs louder than I’ve ever heard."
    "Aaron叹着气，比我以往听过的都要沉重。"

# game/b13.rpy:1416
translate schinese chapter13_7e193d6b:

    # Aa "I won’t make excuses for myself. I won’t even try to sugar coat it saying, ‘we did what we had to do.’"
    Aa "我不会为自己的所作所为开脱什么。我更不会用所谓的『必须要做的事』来粉饰这种行为。"

# game/b13.rpy:1417
translate schinese chapter13_74abe9db:

    # Aa "We were a band of thieves who did what we wanted, when we wanted.{w} I’m ashamed to admit it, but that’s what we were."
    Aa "我们曾是一帮窃贼，为非作歹、肆意妄为。{w}尽管我耻于承认，但是我们的过去就是如此。"

# game/b13.rpy:1418
translate schinese chapter13_b2a6ed2c:

    # cyr "..."
    cyr "..."

# game/b13.rpy:1420
translate schinese chapter13_3ca5df46:

    # Aa "Sorry. I prattled on for a while, didn’t I?{w} I just... It was eating at me. I wanted you to know who I really am."
    Aa "真是抱歉。我自言自语好一会儿了吧？{w}我只是...这种感觉一直蚕食着我的思绪。我只是想让你看清我的真实面目。"

# game/b13.rpy:1421
translate schinese chapter13_9854abc5:

    # "He’s shaking again, just like when we were with Vita when I got my memories back."
    "他又颤抖起来，样子就好像那时看到和Vita一起，刚恢复记忆的我一样。"

# game/b13.rpy:1422
translate schinese chapter13_2846d338:

    # "It takes me a moment to say anything.{w} It is a lot of information to take in all at once."
    "我思索了一会儿才想好要说点什么。{w}一下子让我接受的信息太多了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1423
translate schinese chapter13_8f58d70b:

    # "I don’t want to disregard everything he’s told me, though."
    "不过我不想忽视他向我坦白的所有这些过往。"

# game/b13.rpy:1424
translate schinese chapter13_d7aafbda:

    # cyr "... So, what changed?"
    cyr "...那么，是什么改变了呢？"

# game/b13.rpy:1426
translate schinese chapter13_40e15a40:

    # Aa "What do you mean?"
    Aa "你的意思是？"

# game/b13.rpy:1427
translate schinese chapter13_09abe6cd:

    # cyr "You’ve been the nicest person I’ve met since I got out of Current.{w} Something must have happened for you to end up like this."
    cyr "自我从Current逃脱之后，你是我遇见过的最好的人。{w}你身上一定是发生了什么变故才让你有了如此的改变。"

# game/b13.rpy:1428
translate schinese chapter13_c2f51abf:

    # cyr "Life dealt you a bad hand. I think you have the right to be angry about it.{w} Granted, some things you told me were... not good."
    cyr "命运派给你一手烂牌。我认为你有权利对此表达自己的愤怒。{w}不过当然，你告诉我的那些...并不算什么好事。"

# game/b13.rpy:1430
translate schinese chapter13_d36bdc70_1:

    # Aa "..."
    Aa "..."

# game/b13.rpy:1432
translate schinese chapter13_6d74c502:

    # "I put a reassuring hand on his shoulder. He flinches."
    "我把手掌轻轻抚上他的肩膀，摩挲着。而他身子一颤缩了起来。"

# game/b13.rpy:1433
translate schinese chapter13_ee5e1ed1:

    # cyr "Do you feel bad about what you’ve done?"
    cyr "你对自己的所作所为感到难过吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:1434
translate schinese chapter13_15162dca:

    # Aa "More than you could know.{w} I wish I could just forget it all, but that’d be cowardly."
    Aa "比你想象的还要难过。{w}我多希望我能忘掉那一切，但这样真的太孬种了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1435
translate schinese chapter13_de20a1b8:

    # cyr "Yes, it would be. But you know what isn’t? Admitting that what you were doing was wrong and growing to be a better person."
    cyr "是，话是这么说。但你知道怎样做才不是懦弱的行为不是吗？勇敢承认自己犯下的错误，向着更好的一面去成长。"

# game/b13.rpy:1436
translate schinese chapter13_43094f4a:

    # cyr "I mean, for fuck’s sake. You were scraping by after the apocalypse, Aaron.{w} That’s not something a lot of people could handle."
    cyr "我的意思就是...去他妈的。Aaron，七星事件后你就像一叶孤舟在乱世中沉浮。{w}并不是所有人都能撑下来的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1438
translate schinese chapter13_9dce5592:

    # Aa "You say that, but I can still remember it all clear as day.{w} I can’t sleep some nights. I just think about it."
    Aa "我知道你会这么说的啦，但我仍能回忆起所有的一切。{w}有些夜晚我辗转反侧，就只是困在那里无法自拔。"

# game/b13.rpy:1439
translate schinese chapter13_f069cf30:

    # cyr "Have you been keeping this to yourself all this time?"
    cyr "这么久以来你一直都隐瞒着吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:1441
translate schinese chapter13_0c65d364:

    # Aa "Yeah, for the most part. But that’s only because everyone else knew where I came from."
    Aa "是啊，大多数情况下都是这样。不过这只是因为其他人都知道我的出身。"

# game/b13.rpy:1442
translate schinese chapter13_2f906f5b:

    # Aa "I was worried the most about you finding out.{w} I couldn’t live with myself if you started seeing me as some kind of monster."
    Aa "我最担心的是你最终会发现。{w}如果你把我看作怪物，我真的无法原谅自己。"

# game/b13.rpy:1443
translate schinese chapter13_e691ef34:

    # cyr "Why would I think that?"
    cyr "我为什么要这样想？"

# game/b13.rpy:1445
translate schinese chapter13_7b3a1757:

    # Aa "Because I did-"
    Aa "因为我做了——"

# game/b13.rpy:1446
translate schinese chapter13_c507dbf2:

    # cyr "You did bad things, Aaron. You fucked up.{w} But you’re trying to atone for that, right?"
    cyr "做了无法被原谅的事，Aaron。你搞砸了一切。{w}但是你正在尽力为自己的过错赎罪，不是吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:1448
translate schinese chapter13_9f79eda1:

    # Aa "Y-yes... I am. But I don’t think it’ll ever be enough."
    Aa "是—是的...我是在做。但是我不认为这样做就够了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1449
translate schinese chapter13_7180ee8c:

    # cyr "It might not be, but you’re trying. That’s better than some people I know who have done a lot less."
    cyr "也许不够，但你仍在努力尝试。这已经比我认识的某些人要好多了，他们所做的挽救要少得多。"

# game/b13.rpy:1451
translate schinese chapter13_86301fdb:

    # "He starts to tremble, and I take that as my cue to give him the best side hug I can."
    "他毛绒绒的身躯颤抖着，我把这看作某种暗示，于是我尽我所能给了他一个最深情的拥抱。"

# game/b13.rpy:1452
translate schinese chapter13_036d76a1:

    # cyr "I wouldn’t be here if it wasn’t for you, Aaron. I hope you know how happy you’ve made me."
    cyr "如果不是因为有你，Aaron，我就不可能出现在这里了。我希望你能知道你让我多么开心。"

# game/b13.rpy:1453
translate schinese chapter13_83d5c4ce:

    # "I can’t see his face, but I can hear him whimper as he tries to return my hug."
    "我看不到他的表情，但我能捕捉到他正试着环抱我时发出的呜咽声。"

# game/b13.rpy:1466
translate schinese chapter13_975afbd9:

    # "We sit quietly for a while.{w} Eventually, the fire goes out, almost leaving us in the dark."
    "我们靠着彼此静静地坐着。{w}等到最后一根柴火燃尽，我们的身影被夜晚淹没在了星空之下。"

# game/b13.rpy:1467
translate schinese chapter13_9b79da9a:

    # "The moon is bright tonight, which gives us enough light to look around."
    "一轮圆月高悬在夜空之上，清亮的月光穿过茂密的树冠，在我们周围洒下斑驳的光影。"

# game/b13.rpy:1468
translate schinese chapter13_c96f4c7b:

    # "I can see Aaron wipe his face with his bandana after we separate."
    "恋恋不舍的相拥分开后，我看到Aaron用他的方巾拭了拭自己的脸。"

# game/b13.rpy:1469
translate schinese chapter13_fc9d92b4:

    # Aa "Man... I thought I couldn’t get more pathetic."
    Aa "啊...我觉得自己已经可悲到不可救药了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1470
translate schinese chapter13_fecdac68:

    # cyr "Don’t say that. You’re not pathetic at all."
    cyr "别这么说。你一点也不。"

# game/b13.rpy:1471
translate schinese chapter13_32689114:

    # Aa "You say that, but sometimes I’m not so sure."
    Aa "知道你会这么说，不过有时我还是会怀疑自己。"

# game/b13.rpy:1472
translate schinese chapter13_cd872177:

    # cyr "When push comes to shove, I’ll be there to pick you back up."
    cyr "实在不行的话，还有我在你身边呢。"

# game/b13.rpy:1473
translate schinese chapter13_4ce95f51:

    # Aa "Cyrus..."
    Aa "Cyrus..."

# game/b13.rpy:1475
translate schinese chapter13_e21a0f07:

    # Aa "You remind me a lot of Xavier, in a way."
    Aa "你多少让我想起了Xavier。"

# game/b13.rpy:1476
translate schinese chapter13_2b3848ac:

    # "That catches me off guard."
    "这下轮到我措手不及了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1477
translate schinese chapter13_77a9e281:

    # cyr "What do you mean?"
    cyr "什么意思？"

# game/b13.rpy:1478
translate schinese chapter13_5d4a270b:

    # Aa "You asked me earlier that something had to have changed, right?"
    Aa "你之前问过我，一定是有什么改变了，不是吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:1479
translate schinese chapter13_6f1fd81f:

    # "I nod, letting Aaron know I’m going to keep listening."
    "我点点头，示意Aaron我想继续听下去。"

# game/b13.rpy:1480
translate schinese chapter13_a5798904:

    # Aa "It was a few years after we left the orphanage.{w} We were a bit notorious, I’ll tell you what."
    Aa "那是我们离开孤儿院之后的几年。{w}你猜怎么着，在那时我们的『名气』就已经远扬了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1481
translate schinese chapter13_deffd001:

    # Aa "Sometimes we got a little too brave for our own good.{w} Part of that was leading raids into more developed cities."
    Aa "为了攫取更多利益，有时我们的胆量大到敢于铤而走险。{w}比如牵头去劫掠更发达的城市。"

# game/b13.rpy:1482
translate schinese chapter13_1aa964de:

    # Aa "There’s a town to the east of Tencia, called Steine. It wasn’t as advanced as Tencia, but it was pretty close."
    Aa "Tencia东部有一座叫做Steine的小镇。它没发展到Tencia那种程度，不过也算是很接近了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1483
translate schinese chapter13_b832c055:

    # Aa "We decided to raise hell in a place that had never seen it before for no reason other than to prove a point."
    Aa "我们决定去没见识过我们厉害的地方肆虐一番，不为别的，只是为了证明我们有这个能力。"

# game/b13.rpy:1484
translate schinese chapter13_648cf6a2:

    # Aa "During our first raid, however, something happened that changed our lives forever."
    Aa "然而在那个地方首次行动时发生的事情永远地改变了我们的命运。"

# game/b13.rpy:1496
translate schinese chapter13_fcbbe67d:

    # u "H-hey, you!{w=0.3} Can you hear me?{w=0.3} Please help me!"
    u "呃—嘿！那边的人！{w=0.3}你听得到嘛？{w=0.3}请帮帮我！"

# game/b13.rpy:1497
translate schinese chapter13_788e40f7:

    # Aa "Huh?"
    Aa "嗯哼？"

# game/b13.rpy:1498
translate schinese chapter13_b2ead777:

    # "I grunted in the direction of the soft voice."
    "我打了个响鼻，朝那发出绵软声音的地方望去。"

# game/b13.rpy:1499
translate schinese chapter13_6536b8a1:

    # "A small white-haired human jogged up to me.{w} He’s gasping for breath. They were absolutely filthy with completely tattered clothes."
    "一位衣衫褴褛的瘦小白发人类喘着粗气，慢步向我跑过来。"

# game/b13.rpy:1500
translate schinese chapter13_37ec5492:

    # "He must have been desperate if he came to me for help."
    "Ta一定是走投无路了，才昏头想要找我帮忙。"

# game/b13.rpy:1501
translate schinese chapter13_186ce813:

    # Aa "...You shouldn’t be here. Don’t you know there’s a raid going on?"
    Aa "...你不该待在这里。难道你不知道此处正遭受袭击么？"

# game/b13.rpy:1502
translate schinese chapter13_2403a6fd:

    # u "That’s how I was able to escape.{w} Can you help me out of here? After that, I won’t bother you ever again!"
    u "我就是趁此逃脱的。{w}你能帮我离开这里么？离开后，我保证不会继续麻烦你！"

# game/b13.rpy:1503
translate schinese chapter13_83d16732:

    # "When they lifted their head up to look at me, I thought they were winking at me. One of their eyes was closed."
    "Ta抬起头望向我，我想Ta是在向我眨眼，不过其中一只眼紧闭着。"

# game/b13.rpy:1504
translate schinese chapter13_89d3d861:

    # u "Please! I don’t have any money or valuables, but I can pay you back in time. I promise!"
    u "求求你！现在我身上虽然没有现金，也没有什么值钱的物品，但帮我离开后我会付钱的，我保证！"

# game/b13.rpy:1505
translate schinese chapter13_0ce4b7ef:

    # "The more I looked him over, the more I realized just how beat up he was."
    "我越是仔细打量Ta，越意识到Ta的身躯是多么残破。"

# game/b13.rpy:1507
translate schinese chapter13_6126be70:

    # Kar "Hey, Aaron! What the hell are you doing? We got shit to beat in!"
    Kar "嘿，Aaron！你他娘的在干什么呢？我们还有一堆破事要做！"

# game/b13.rpy:1508
translate schinese chapter13_82bbf6b1:

    # "My second-in-command yelled for me from the other side of the street, pipe in hand."
    "我的副手挥舞着手中的管子，在街对面冲我大喊道。"

# game/b13.rpy:1509
translate schinese chapter13_6abf5bc1:

    # u "Wait, did you all start this? You have to get out of here!"
    u "等等，这场袭击是你们发起的？你们得赶紧逃！"

# game/b13.rpy:1510
translate schinese chapter13_15e2c33b:

    # Aa "And why’s that?"
    Aa "为什么要逃？"

# game/b13.rpy:1511
translate schinese chapter13_07be36e4:

    # u "Because Resoom is stationed here!"
    u "因为这里是Resoom的据点！"

# game/b13.rpy:1512
translate schinese chapter13_a7640e67:

    # Aa "What?!"
    Aa "什么？！"

# game/b13.rpy:1513
translate schinese chapter13_6a5cc0e3:

    # "I looked around at the damage we’d done, and just how much shit we were in."
    "我环顾四周，看着我们造成的破坏，突然意识到自己摊上了大事。"

# game/b13.rpy:1514
translate schinese chapter13_6fc05e99:

    # "The small human grabbed my paw and then tried to direct me away."
    "那瘦小的人类抓住我的爪子，试图拉我离开。"

# game/b13.rpy:1515
translate schinese chapter13_8d8f41ca:

    # u "If you don’t get out of here, they’re going to kill you. Please!"
    u "如果你现在不跑的话，他们肯定会杀了你的！"

# game/b13.rpy:1516
translate schinese chapter13_77d49b9b:

    # "I’m 6’ 8” tall. This human couldn’t be any taller than 5 feet, 10 inches.{w} He was scared of the situation at hand, but fearless of me."
    "我身高两米出头。这个人类顶天也就一米八的样子。他因周围的状况而惶恐不已，但对我却丝毫不怕。"

# game/b13.rpy:1517
translate schinese chapter13_b1d4a1fd:

    # "I had never been more confused in my life."
    "怪事，我从来没有这么迷糊过。"

# game/b13.rpy:1519
translate schinese chapter13_0f264ff7:

    # "Sirens wailed in the distance.{w} The human tried pulling me even harder."
    "远处，警报声狂鸣。{w}那人类拽我拽得更狠了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1520
translate schinese chapter13_f39a3f6e:

    # Aa "...Ugh, dammit! Karin, round everyone up! We’re getting out of here!"
    Aa "...呃，该死！Karin，把大家召集起来！我们得赶紧离开这里！"

# game/b13.rpy:1538
translate schinese chapter13_652735db:

    # "We were back at our desert camp for the night, a good few miles south from Steine."
    "当晚我们回到了沙漠中的营地，此处就位于Steine以南的几里开外。"

# game/b13.rpy:1539
translate schinese chapter13_f6a5b969:

    # "We could still see a cloud of smoke coming over the horizon, but I was pretty sure we ran far enough away that they wouldn’t be able to find us."
    "虽然仍可以望见远方地平线冒起的烟火，但我确信我们已经跑得足够远，他们是绝对找不到我们的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1540
translate schinese chapter13_da7c23f2:

    # "I tried to do a headcount.{w} I was disappointed when I came up short."
    "我清点了人数。{w}十分沮丧地发现少了几个人。"

# game/b13.rpy:1541
translate schinese chapter13_3b196e07:

    # "Five of us didn’t make it out. Their deaths were on my selfish hands."
    "有五位同伴没能逃出来。他们就这么因为我的自私死了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1545
translate schinese chapter13_3ee3ded3:

    # Reg "So... Do you mind telling me who you are? Where you came from?"
    Reg "所以...你介意告诉我们你从哪儿来？到底是谁么？"

# game/b13.rpy:1548
translate schinese chapter13_39b406b2:

    # Lan "I’ve never seen a human with white hair before."
    Lan "我从未见过满头白发的人类。"

# game/b13.rpy:1549
translate schinese chapter13_c857063a:

    # "They both were treating the person we wound up taking care of.{w} We didn’t have a lot of medical supplies, but thankfully most of his wounds seemed to be old."
    "他们正对那人类进行紧张的施救。{w}虽然我们没什么医疗补给，但好在他身上大多是旧伤。"

# game/b13.rpy:1550
translate schinese chapter13_06659e72:

    # "After he took a swig of water, he finally answered."
    "在猛喝了一大口水后，他终于回答道。"

# game/b13.rpy:1554
translate schinese chapter13_c9110bd7:

    # u "Yes, of course. Thank you for taking me in, by the way."
    u "我会告诉你们的。顺带一提，谢谢你们带我离开。"

# game/b13.rpy:1555
translate schinese chapter13_fd8fd332:

    # Xav "My name is Xavier. Xavier Sol."
    Xav "我的名字是Xavier。Xavier Sol。"

# game/b13.rpy:1556
translate schinese chapter13_829132cd:

    # Xav "I was a resident in Resoom. I actually just escaped a couple days ago."
    Xav "我是Resoom的住民。实际上我是两天前逃出来的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1558
translate schinese chapter13_d035c19c:

    # Reg "Escaped?{w=0.3} From a hospital?"
    Reg "逃？{w=0.3}为什么要从医院里逃出来？"

# game/b13.rpy:1559
translate schinese chapter13_d025978a:

    # Xav "...How much time do you all have?"
    Xav "...resoom找上门来前你们还有多少时间？"
