# game/b13.rpy:1564
translate schinese chapter13_0e29ce78:

    # "I grunted before I got up and sat next to them."
    "我咕哝了一声，坐至他身旁。"

# game/b13.rpy:1565
translate schinese chapter13_d97a8bed:

    # Aa "Just how much shit have we gotten into?"
    Aa "...就先说我们到底惹上了怎样的大麻烦吧？"

# game/b13.rpy:1567
translate schinese chapter13_8130cc24:

    # Xav "You don’t know the half of it."
    Xav "那你怕是一无所知。"

# game/b13.rpy:1568
translate schinese chapter13_3bda8d3d:

    # "The human explained all of his experiences over the past hundred or so years. I didn’t believe him at first."
    "人类解释了他过去百年里的经历。起先，我并不相信。"

# game/b13.rpy:1569
translate schinese chapter13_5b4d43ab:

    # "Given his appearance, however, I eventually gave in."
    "但看着他的样子，我最终还是信服。"

# game/b13.rpy:1570
translate schinese chapter13_3b9b1089:

    # "Reggie held his chin in thought."
    "Reggie摸着下巴，思考着。"

# game/b13.rpy:1574
translate schinese chapter13_ef23d54b:

    # Reg "So the ‘saviors of the land’ are actually just a public black market?"
    Reg "所以『这片大陆的救星』实际上是个公共黑市？"

# game/b13.rpy:1575
translate schinese chapter13_6285fe3e:

    # "Reggie sighed before he shook his head."
    "Reggie叹了口气，摇了摇头。"

# game/b13.rpy:1577
translate schinese chapter13_8f573b17:

    # Reg "Glad I didn’t end up working for them after all."
    Reg "还好我最终没有去为他们工作。"

# game/b13.rpy:1578
translate schinese chapter13_b0a8043a:

    # Xav "You believe me?"
    Xav "你相信我？"

# game/b13.rpy:1582
translate schinese chapter13_46991353:

    # Reg "It’s hard not to, particularly with your eye."
    Reg "很难不相信，特别是看你眼睛这幅模样。"

# game/b13.rpy:1583
translate schinese chapter13_a62ced69:

    # "Xavier held his hand over his closed eye."
    "Xavier用手捂住他闭上的那只眼。"

# game/b13.rpy:1585
translate schinese chapter13_8e1e6c22:

    # Reg "You’d have to be pretty committed to pretend to having had your eye harvested."
    Reg "你不得不承认，假装眼珠子被挖掉还是太难了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1586
translate schinese chapter13_18720fcd:

    # "My blood started to boil. Yet another aspect of the world who takes advantage of the vulnerable."
    "我的血液沸腾了——鱼肉弱势群体，这世界的又一暗面。"

# game/b13.rpy:1587
translate schinese chapter13_fe56e54c:

    # Xav "I appreciate you looking at it. I haven’t been able to clean it since I left."
    Xav "感谢你注意到了这点。实际上自从我出逃以来，我都没法做眼部清洗。"

# game/b13.rpy:1589
translate schinese chapter13_b531dda5:

    # Reg "I didn’t do much. Honestly, we should get you to a professional if we can."
    Reg "我能做的不多，实话说，我们应该带你去找专业的医疗人员。"

# game/b13.rpy:1591
translate schinese chapter13_7883e6f7:

    # "Reggie turned toward me."
    "Reggie转向我。"

# game/b13.rpy:1592
translate schinese chapter13_a47aa009:

    # Reg "What do you think? We can’t take care of him with what we have currently. We can barely get by as it is."
    Reg "你怎么想的？现在我们可没法照顾他。要知道我们维持现状都勉强。"

# game/b13.rpy:1593
translate schinese chapter13_6e8819e5:

    # Aa "You don’t have to tell me that. I’m well aware."
    Aa "犯不着你告诉我这点。我很清楚。"

# game/b13.rpy:1594
translate schinese chapter13_cb8f8957:

    # Xav "Oh, you don’t have to take care of me. I’ll be fine."
    Xav "哦，你们没必要照顾我，我会没事的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1598
translate schinese chapter13_baeb5e01:

    # "Xavier got up and then patted his dusty clothes."
    "Xavier站起身来，拍了拍Ta满是尘土的衣物。"

# game/b13.rpy:1599
translate schinese chapter13_db200301:

    # Xav "I’m glad you took me in this direction. I have a contact I’ve been meaning to meet."
    Xav "很高兴你们把我带到这里。我有一个联系人，我一直试图和Ta会面来着。"

# game/b13.rpy:1600
translate schinese chapter13_60142e8e:

    # "He set his sights on the desert wastelands to the east."
    "他放眼向东部的沙漠荒地望去。"

