# game/b13.rpy:1645
translate schinese chapter13_910ccd62:

    # "Xavier explained the gravity of the situation at hand to us, along with who broke him out of Resoom."
    "Xavier解释了我们目前面临处境的严重性，以及到底是谁把他从Resoom里救了出来。"

# game/b13.rpy:1646
translate schinese chapter13_094d0c78:

    # "He told us that for the past two years, he’s been secretly in contact with a spy who had managed to climb his way up to try to break him out."
    "他告诉我们这两年来，他一直在秘密地与一位间谍联系，企图逃走。"

# game/b13.rpy:1647
translate schinese chapter13_9a081e3b:

    # "There was a mishap right at the end, however. The spy got himself killed while Xavier tried to get away."
