# game/b13.rpy:1648
translate schinese chapter13_c498346b:

    # "He couldn’t make it out of the city without getting caught, so he’s been in hiding, waiting for an opportunity to escape."
    "而他独自一人无法逃离这座城市，因此他一直在躲藏，等待机会逃跑。"

# game/b13.rpy:1649
translate schinese chapter13_7d484a21:

    # "We just happened to be at the right place at the right time."
    "我们则是恰好出现在了正确的时间和地点。"

# game/b13.rpy:1650
translate schinese chapter13_ab2bc28c:

    # "The human started to unravel a bit now that he’s had a chance to breathe."
    "说完，Xavier终于稍稍放松，喘息起来。"

# game/b13.rpy:1651
translate schinese chapter13_9d7757c5:

    # Xav "If my body let me move right, Grant would still be alive. I’m so damn slow now."
    Xav "如果我的身体能正常行动，Grant就不会死了。我的动作实在是太慢了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1652
translate schinese chapter13_a0a16463:

