translate schinese chapter13_c6b03875:

    # Reg "Don’t diminish his sacrifice by making yourself feel bad. You’re disrespecting him."
    Reg "不要自责，你这是在贬损他为你作出的牺牲，那是对他的不尊重。"

# game/b13.rpy:1660
translate schinese chapter13_70bbb1c9:

    # Xav "You say that, but..."
    Xav "说是这么说，但..."

