translate schinese chapter13_23503d94:

    # Lan "I’m sure he just wanted to help you. I mean, he wouldn’t have gone through all that if he didn’t right?"
    Lan "我确信他只是想要帮你。我的意思是，如果他没有意愿，也不会做这些事情。"

# game/b13.rpy:1665
translate schinese chapter13_a86005be:

    # Xav "I know, I know... But..."
    Xav "我知道，我知道...可是..."

# game/b13.rpy:1666
translate schinese chapter13_edee8a91:

    # "Xavier’s gaze turned toward me.{w} Their one eye widened in surprise."
