# game/b13.rpy:1700
translate schinese chapter13_938b426d:

    # Aa "Xavier was the kind of guy to put others over himself, even when he was in a bad state."
    Aa "Xavier是把他人置于自身之上的那类人，即便自己身处糟糕的状态。"

# game/b13.rpy:1701
translate schinese chapter13_29f4e41d:

