    # Aa "I, uh, hope that learning more about me doesn’t scare you... or anything."
    Aa "我，呃，希望对我的深入了解不会吓到你...或是怎么样。"

# game/b13.rpy:1713
translate schinese chapter13_b811edca:

    # cyr "Aaron, you don’t have to worry about that. You’re, like, my best friend."
    cyr "Aaron，不必担心这个问题。你就像，不，就是我最好的朋友。"

# game/b13.rpy:1714
translate schinese chapter13_29a2ba32:

    # cyr "The fact that you felt comfortable enough to tell me everything means a lot to me."
    cyr "你可以放心地告诉我一切，不仅能让你好受一些，也让我很高兴。"

# game/b13.rpy:1716
translate schinese chapter13_de868f07:

    # Aa "It was mainly out of fear, if anything."
    Aa "如果有的话，主要是由于我的恐惧吧。"

