translate schinese chapter13_b0321e6f:

    # "Without hesitating, he takes a pill bottle out of his Axiom.{w} He pops a couple into his mouth before swallowing."
    "不假思索，他从Axiom中取出一个药瓶。{w}他倒出两粒丢进嘴巴然后咽下了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1739
translate schinese chapter13_71873b5a:

    # Aa "Feel free to wake me up in the morning if I oversleep, but I’ll try to set an alarm for us."
    Aa "如果我睡过头了，早上随时都可以叫醒我，不过我也会给我俩定一个闹钟。"

# game/b13.rpy:1740
