    # cyr "Thank you for telling me, Aaron.{w} Good night, you big softy."
    cyr "Aaron，谢谢你能和我倾诉这么多。{w}晚安啦，你个大暖男。"

# game/b13.rpy:1760
translate schinese chapter13_c3a73d1d:

    # Aa "Hmph. Good night, Cyrus."
    Aa "嗯哼。好梦，Cyrus。"

