# game/b13.rpy:1781
translate schinese chapter13_7f9553b9:

    # "I can still picture scenes of this town in its heyday, with bustling streets and community."
    "我仍能想象出这个小镇最美好时候的样子，街道和社区熙熙攘攘充满生气。"

# game/b13.rpy:1782
translate schinese chapter13_889c1b58:

    # "Now, at this point most of the buildings are showing their age, with many falling into disrepair."
    "但现在，大多数建筑都早已在时间无情的冲刷下显得年久失修，很多楼塌了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1783
translate schinese chapter13_7a2a7de7:

    # "It’s a small miracle that there are still any buildings left standing."
    "不过经历这么漫长的岁月仍有一些建筑物得以保留下来，这可真是一个小小的奇迹。"

# game/b13.rpy:1784
translate schinese chapter13_d9045d13:

    # "There aren’t any windows left in the buildings, and the one’s that are still there are absolutely covered in faded graffiti."
    "这些建筑的窗户鲜有幸存，就算有那么一两个幸运儿，也绝对会有褪色的涂鸦覆盖其上。"

# game/b13.rpy:1785
translate schinese chapter13_91f76e59:

    # "I guess mass looting makes sense."
    "我想这里可能发生了大规模的抢劫。"

# game/b13.rpy:1787
translate schinese chapter13_8059071d:

    # "I stand over a group of makeshift graves."
    "我来到一个乱葬岗前站定。"

# game/b13.rpy:1788
translate schinese chapter13_fc79b69d:

    # "It takes me some time to process it all."
    "我需要一些时间来处理所见的一切。"

# game/b13.rpy:1789
translate schinese chapter13_ccd12df2:

    # "There aren’t any names or gravestones, I have no idea who these people are."
    "这里没有名字，没有墓碑，就算有心想去了解这些逝者也无从下手。"

# game/b13.rpy:1790
translate schinese chapter13_17a86e2d:

    # "No one has for centuries."
    "也许，我是这几个世纪唯一来看望他们的人吧。"

# game/b13.rpy:1791
translate schinese chapter13_0735d62a:

    # "At the very least, I can pay my respects, if only to make myself feel just a little bit better."
    "但至少，我还可以献上我的敬意，哪怕这么做只是为了让自己心里好受一点罢了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1792
translate schinese chapter13_e8ea77c3:

    # "Everything is just about how I would have expected it, or rather how I should have expected.{w} It’s been three hundred years after all."
    "一切都和我预想的一样，或者说我早应该预料到是这样，毕竟这都已经过去三百年了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1793
translate schinese chapter13_abea456a:

    # "Still, it does make me a little sad to see the town I grew up in falling apart like this."
    "不过，看到我长大的小镇就这样分崩离析，我着实有些难过。"

# game/b13.rpy:1795
translate schinese chapter13_9ae49a09:

    # "When I glance at Aaron, he looks worried."
    "我瞥了一眼Aaron，发现他的脸上写满了担忧。"

# game/b13.rpy:1796
translate schinese chapter13_829e6f20:

    # "This was my idea to begin with, I don’t want Aaron to think it was a bad one."
    "来这里是我的想法，我可不想让Aaron认为这是个坏主意。"

# game/b13.rpy:1797
translate schinese chapter13_dfc072be:

    # "With no more hesitation, I take my helmet off before getting out of the sidecar."
    "我没有再犹豫，摘掉头盔，走下车来。"

# game/b13.rpy:1798
translate schinese chapter13_54609194:

    # "I take in a deep breath of crisp, what used to be Vermont air."
    "我深吸一口清冽的、曾属于佛蒙特州的空气。"

# game/b13.rpy:1799
translate schinese chapter13_6a724852:

    # "I’m happy to see that the pine trees are still alive and well, it makes this feel just a little bit like home."
    "看到这里的松树仍旧长势良好，我很高兴，总算是有了点家的味道。"

# game/b13.rpy:1800
translate schinese chapter13_493c73ef:

    # "Despite how barren everything is, I’m still feeling nostalgic."
    "尽管这片大地是那么的荒芜，但我仍然感到十分怀念。"

# game/b13.rpy:1802
translate schinese chapter13_ea356fd2:

    # Aa "How are you feeling-?"
    Aa "你感觉如何—？"

# game/b13.rpy:1803
translate schinese chapter13_fe36a405:

    # cyr "It’s been so long since I was last here.{w} I wouldn’t be surprised if I forgot how to get to my house."
    cyr "我已经很久没有来过这里了。{w}如果我忘了回家的路，我也不会奇怪。"

# game/b13.rpy:1805
translate schinese chapter13_a698bdd9:

    # Aa "Well, we’ve got a lot of time on our hands to find it."
    Aa "没事，我们有大把的时间。"

# game/b13.rpy:1806
translate schinese chapter13_c0fda923:

    # cyr "We sure do.{w} I think I’ve got a better idea. Want to take a trip with me down memory lane?"
    cyr "我们当然会找到它的。{w}而且我想我有一个更好的主意。想与我一起来场回忆之旅么？"

# game/b13.rpy:1808
translate schinese chapter13_b1435500:

    # Aa "Of course, Cyrus. Lead the way."
    Aa "当然，Cyrus，请带路吧。"

# game/b13.rpy:1810
translate schinese chapter13_2ddb6385:

    # "I try shaking my uneasiness off."
    "我试着甩掉心头的不安。"

# game/b13.rpy:1811
translate schinese chapter13_d3a95fa9:

    # "Who knows, maybe it’ll be fun giving a good friend a tour of the place."
    "天知道，也许让好朋友参观一下这个地方会很有趣。"

# game/b13.rpy:1819
translate schinese chapter13_90f678b6:

    # "After we walk for a couple blocks, I point to a building at the top of a hill.{w} Even from here I can see just how dilapidated it really is."
    "走过几个街区后，我指了指山顶上的一座大建筑。{w}即使隔着这么远，我也能看得出它变得有多么破旧。"

# game/b13.rpy:1820
translate schinese chapter13_46f72fc0:

    # cyr "That was my old elementary school.{w} It wasn’t very big, so it only went up to fifth grade. The middle school was a separate building in town."
    cyr "那里是我以前的小学。{w}因为那块地方不是很大，所以学校只负责教到5年级，而我的中学则是位于镇上的一栋独立建筑。"

# game/b13.rpy:1822
translate schinese chapter13_76282bf3:

    # Aa "Oh wow... Can we go inside?"
    Aa "哇哦...我们可以进去看看吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:1823
translate schinese chapter13_3fdd1167:

    # cyr "I don’t see why not. How come?"
    cyr "有何不可，不过你为什么想进去参观？"

# game/b13.rpy:1825
translate schinese chapter13_734abacc:

    # Aa "I’ve never been in a school before. I’m kind of curious."
    Aa "只是对此有些好奇，毕竟我以前从没上过学。"

# game/b13.rpy:1826
translate schinese chapter13_cbfcd90a:

    # cyr "As good of a reason as any. Who knows? Maybe we’ll find some ghosts."
    cyr "很充足的理由，走吧，说不定我们还会在里边找到一些鬼魂呢。"

# game/b13.rpy:1828
translate schinese chapter13_0f428306:

    # Aa "Do you believe in them?"
    Aa "你相信世上有鬼么？"

# game/b13.rpy:1829
translate schinese chapter13_af3025a8:

    # cyr "If this world has taught me anything, it’s that nothing is impossible."
    cyr "如果要说这个世界教会了我什么的话，那便是没有什么是不可能的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1831
translate schinese chapter13_87c12b69:

    # Aa "Well said."
    Aa "说得好。"

# game/b13.rpy:1839
translate schinese chapter13_286fc022:

    # "It doesn’t take long for us to break into the school.{w} The doors have been rusted shut for so long that even I could push them open."
    "没过多久我们就闯进了学校，大门早已生锈得破败不堪，连我都轻易推开。"

# game/b13.rpy:1840
translate schinese chapter13_5dbb60d5:

    # "I let Aaron lead the way inside, answering any questions he asks."
    "我一边让Aaron先进去带路，一边回答他提出的任何问题。"

# game/b13.rpy:1849
translate schinese chapter13_24ee6478:

    # Aa "These chairs are really small..."
    Aa "这些椅子可真小..."

# game/b13.rpy:1850
translate schinese chapter13_f92e9d47:

    # cyr "This is the kindergarten room. Kids are pretty young when they start."
    cyr "当然啦，毕竟在这里可是幼儿园的房间，小孩儿个子能大到哪去。"

# game/b13.rpy:1852
translate schinese chapter13_c3d6eaee:

    # Aa "Hard to imagine anyone could fit in them. My hand is bigger than some of these chairs."
    Aa "很难想象有人能坐得下这么小的椅子，我的手都比这些椅子大。"

# game/b13.rpy:1853
translate schinese chapter13_28774177:

    # cyr "To be fair, you are a rather large lad."
    cyr "说句公道话，你可是个相当高大的『小伙子』。"

# game/b13.rpy:1855
translate schinese chapter13_667f2fdf:

    # Aa "Another fair point."
    Aa "那确实。"

# game/b13.rpy:1863
translate schinese chapter13_2701bc36:

    # "We make our way through the various classrooms."
    "我们在各种教室间穿行着。"

# game/b13.rpy:1864
translate schinese chapter13_0e9a22f3:

    # "There’s a lot of stuff people left behind that piques Aaron’s interest."
    "教室中的大量遗留物品引起了Aaron的兴趣。"

# game/b13.rpy:1870
translate schinese chapter13_b5bd849a:

    # Aa "Would it be disrespectful to take anything here?"
    Aa "我能拿走一些吗？这样会不会不太尊重？"

# game/b13.rpy:1871
translate schinese chapter13_bb6fbdd5:

    # cyr "I don’t think so. Beats leaving it here for no one to use."
    cyr "我不这么认为，就算把它们留在这里，我想也没有人会用吧。"

# game/b13.rpy:1873
translate schinese chapter13_1a8bafa2:

    # Aa "I guess you’re right. These are crayons, right?"
    Aa "我想你是对的。我手里的这些是蜡笔对吧？"

# game/b13.rpy:1874
translate schinese chapter13_f3effd74:

    # cyr "Yeah. I bet you might be able to use them. Doubt the markers would work, though."
    cyr "是的。我敢打赌它们还能用，不过，那些记号笔就不知道了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1876
translate schinese chapter13_d5c36e8c:

    # Aa "Oh..."
    Aa "噢..."

# game/b13.rpy:1878
translate schinese chapter13_89551046:

    # "His childlike wonder makes him look right at home here."
    "他那孩子般的好奇心让他如燕归巢。"

# game/b13.rpy:1879
translate schinese chapter13_1bb32384:

    # "I look around the room, eventually finding the desk I used to sit at all those years ago."
    "我环顾房间，最终找到了许多年前我曾经坐过的桌子。"

# game/b13.rpy:1880
translate schinese chapter13_e17f1b2d:

    # "I try my best to sit in it, but it’s very apparent that even I’m too big for these."
    "我尽全力把双腿塞进去，但很显然，这个桌子对我来说还是太小了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1881
translate schinese chapter13_c855fa01:

    # "Still, looking at the faded electronic whiteboard from this angle brings back memories."
    "尽管如此，从这个角度看向那褪色的电子白板还是让我回想起了一些事情。"

# game/b13.rpy:1882
translate schinese chapter13_d1c57c4b:

    # "Like Diana helping me with homework, or telling me about a new cartoon she was into."
    "例如Diana帮我做作业，或者告诉我她最近喜欢的一部新漫画之类的事。"

# game/b13.rpy:1883
translate schinese chapter13_d357042e:

    # cyr "Times really were a lot simpler back then."
    cyr "那些日子可真是轻松惬意啊。"

# game/b13.rpy:1885
translate schinese chapter13_e747ece0:

    # Aa "Huh? What’d you say?"
    Aa "哈？你在说啥？"

# game/b13.rpy:1886
translate schinese chapter13_c2718852:

    # "Aaron is scribbling in a notebook on the teacher’s desk, trying his best not to accidentally tear the old paper."
    "Aaron正在老师办公桌上的笔记本上涂写着什么，能看出他在尽力控制自己下笔的力道以防旧纸被自己不慎撕碎。"

# game/b13.rpy:1887
translate schinese chapter13_d6d2e301:

    # cyr "Nothing. Whatcha doing?"
    cyr "没什么，你在做什么呢？"

# game/b13.rpy:1889
translate schinese chapter13_762b7163:

    # Aa "I don’t have a lot of pens and pencils that still work, so I’m trying out these crayons."
    Aa "这些钢笔、铅笔大多没法用了，所以我正在尝试用这些蜡笔写字。"

# game/b13.rpy:1890
translate schinese chapter13_10be6edf:

    # "I get up from the tiny desk to watch him."
    "我从小桌子上站起来看着他。"

# game/b13.rpy:1892
translate schinese chapter13_fb917df9:

    # Aa "My paws are too big for these things, though.{w} My penmanship is already atrocious as it is."
    Aa "不过我的爪子对于这些纸来说还是太大了，{w}而且我写的字也真是有够丑的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1893
translate schinese chapter13_ceb96ab5:

    # cyr "It just takes practice. Keep it up and I’m sure you’ll get the hang of it."
    cyr "多练就好，坚持下去，我相信你一定会掌握窍门的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1895
translate schinese chapter13_7f5ec46a:

    # Aa "Mind showing me how you write?"
    Aa "能给我示范一下你是怎么写字的吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:1896
translate schinese chapter13_24b457b3:

    # cyr "Sure. Although it’s been a while."
    cyr "当然可以，不过我已经有好一段时间没写过字了。"

# game/b13.rpy:1897
translate schinese chapter13_0cf4e9ed:

    # "I pick out an orange crayon as I try to write my signature."
    "我挑出一个橙色的蜡笔，试着在纸上写下我的签名。"

# game/b13.rpy:1898
translate schinese chapter13_445fcfc1:

    # "{font=font/Rocchy__s_handwriting.ttf}{size=70}Cyrus G. Cantwell."
    "{font=font/Rocchy__s_handwriting.ttf}{size=70}Cyrus G. Cantwell.{/font}"

# game/b13.rpy:1900
translate schinese chapter13_97b866cb:

    # Aa "Oh, wow. You didn’t even hesitate."
    Aa "噢，哇哦。你下笔甚至没有丝毫犹豫。"

# game/b13.rpy:1901
translate schinese chapter13_63d154de:

    # cyr "Guess the muscle memory is still there. We are in the room where I learned cursive, after all."
    cyr "看来我的肌肉记忆还在嘛，毕竟我们就是在这里学的草书。"

# game/b13.rpy:1903
translate schinese chapter13_1e62a8ea:

    # Aa "You promised to teach me sometime, remember?"
    Aa "你答应过我会抽时间教我写字的，还记得吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:1904
translate schinese chapter13_64eadd64:

    # cyr "Of course. Maybe when we get home?"
    cyr "噢当然，要不我们找到家之后再教？"

# game/b13.rpy:1905
translate schinese chapter13_eee70f8a:

    # Aa "Sounds like a deal."
    Aa "听起来不错。"

# game/b13.rpy:1916
translate schinese chapter13_9ed3cc34:

    # cyr "That’s a sandwich shop I used to go to a lot. It eventually became my first summer job."
    cyr "那家三明治店我以前经常去的呢，我的第一份暑假工也是在那里拿到的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1918
translate schinese chapter13_15236110:

    # Aa "Summer job? Like, only working during the summer?"
    Aa "暑假工？是，那种只在暑假才会做的工作？"

# game/b13.rpy:1919
translate schinese chapter13_59a38b44:

    # cyr "Yeah. Back then, when you were still in school, you really only had time to work in the summer."
    cyr "是的，在当时，如果你还在上学的话，你真的只有在暑假才有时间工作。"

# game/b13.rpy:1921
translate schinese chapter13_37ec3b1d:

    # Aa "Oh... Huh. I just figured people did both."
    Aa "哦...这样啊，我以为大家都是又学习又打工呢。"

# game/b13.rpy:1922
translate schinese chapter13_fda44de6:

    # cyr "That was common, too, but I couldn’t hack it."
    cyr "那样的人蛮多啦，但我做不来就是。"

# game/b13.rpy:1923
translate schinese chapter13_2d0e5061:

    # cyr "I just wanted to help my folks out with the bills when I could, was all."
    cyr "那时我只是想力所能及地帮我的家人减轻一下经济负担。"

# game/b13.rpy:1925
translate schinese chapter13_5e5e4dad:

    # Aa "Guess some things never change, huh?"
    Aa "我想有些事情还是永远不会改变的，对吧？"

# game/b13.rpy:1926
translate schinese chapter13_ac3a93a3:

    # cyr "Guess not. Glad to know some things have stayed consistent over the years."
    cyr "也许吧，不过我还是很高兴知道有些事情随时间流逝，仍然不变。"

# game/b13.rpy:1928
translate schinese chapter13_b3d8bf6d:

    # "As I look around the streets, more and more nostalgia floods in."
    "当我环顾街道时，越来越多的怀旧之情涌入心头。"

# game/b13.rpy:1929
translate schinese chapter13_114381a1:

    # "Most of the uneasiness has long since melted away."
    "萦绕心头许久的不安早已散去。"

# game/b13.rpy:1930
translate schinese chapter13_40e654bc:

    # "Despite how barren everything is, I’m glad we came."
    "尽管这里一切看上去是那么荒芜，但我还是很高兴我们来到了这里。"

# game/b13.rpy:1931
translate schinese chapter13_3e82ae10:

    # "I direct us to the road my house was on, letting my memories guide me."
    "深埋在脑海里的记忆，指引着我前往家的方向。"

# game/b13.rpy:1941
translate schinese chapter13_d027fd9f:

    # "We eventually make it to the local park.{w} It was old even when I lived here."
    "最终，我们来到了当地的公园。{w}我记得我们搬到这里时这个公园就已经上了年头。"

# game/b13.rpy:1942
translate schinese chapter13_2f6532bd:

    # "I’m a little sad that almost everything has either toppled over or has rusted too much to be safe."
    "这里的所有东西要么坍塌，要么锈得厉害变得摇摇欲坠，我心底油然生出一丝悲伤。"

# game/b13.rpy:1943
translate schinese chapter13_57eceb9b:

    # "Even the ropes on the swings seemed to have rotted away years ago."
    "甚至吊秋千的绳索也早已在时间的冲刷下变得腐烂不堪。"

# game/b13.rpy:1945
translate schinese chapter13_89bc39ed:

    # Aa "What is this place?"
    Aa "这里是什么地方？"

# game/b13.rpy:1946
translate schinese chapter13_76ecaca8:

    # cyr "It’s an old park for kids to play in. You’ve never seen one?"
    cyr "这里原本是一个旧公园，供孩子们玩耍的地方，你之前从没见过公园么？"

# game/b13.rpy:1948
translate schinese chapter13_72e39a07:

    # Aa "Nope. Back in Aquila, the most we had was the ocean, but the orphanage was too far to walk to it."
    Aa "没有过，在Aquila，看海便是顶天了，但即使如此海边还是离孤儿院太远，仅靠步行很难走到那里。"

# game/b13.rpy:1949
translate schinese chapter13_c5d0d977:

    # cyr "I see. Well, maybe one day we can make a park back home."
    cyr "我明白了，好吧，也许有一天我们可以在家里建一个公园看看。"

# game/b13.rpy:1951
translate schinese chapter13_3620dac2:

    # Aa "Oh? Do you really want to?"
    Aa "哦？你真打算建公园吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:1952
translate schinese chapter13_315bab40:

    # cyr "I dunno. It just feels like a park is a must for a town to be cozy."
    cyr "我不知道，我只是觉得一个小镇要舒适宜人的话，那么公园必不可少。"

# game/b13.rpy:1954
translate schinese chapter13_74dcebfd:

    # Aa "Maybe you should take up architecture. I’m sure you have ideas no one would think of."
    Aa "也许你应该学习下建筑学，我相信你对此肯定有过人的想法。"

# game/b13.rpy:1955
translate schinese chapter13_03f51435:

    # cyr "Ha, maybe. After that, I’ll start recreating stories that no one’s read in centuries for profit."
    cyr "哈，也许吧。在那之后，我说不定还会开始重新创作那些几个世纪以来没有人读过的故事并以此牟利。"

# game/b13.rpy:1956
translate schinese chapter13_eb10cd4f:

    # "That could be extremely lucrative, now that I think about it."
    "现在想想，这可是相当有利可图的活。"

# game/b13.rpy:1958
translate schinese chapter13_d260f095:

    # Aa "Better let me read them too."
    Aa "到时候最好让我也读一读。"

# game/b13.rpy:1959
translate schinese chapter13_9c5e0a93:

    # cyr "You’ll be the first I go to when I need an editor."
    cyr "到那时我想我会需要一个编辑，我会第一个找上你的。"

# game/b13.rpy:1961
translate schinese chapter13_b3110374:

    # Aa "I’d be honored."
    Aa "我很荣幸。"

# game/b13.rpy:1972
translate schinese chapter13_1c21fc9a:

    # "It took no time at all to find my house once we started walking."
    "没走多久，我们便找到了我的家。"

# game/b13.rpy:1973
translate schinese chapter13_b5778c09:

    # "I’m not sure how long I’ve been standing here like this, just staring."
    "不知过了多久，我仍就只是这么站在原地盯着这个地方。"

# game/b13.rpy:1974
translate schinese chapter13_6ff131d2:

    # "If Aaron’s been trying to talk to me, I can’t hear him."
    "也许Aaron一直试着和我说话，但现在的我根本听不见他的声音。"

# game/b13.rpy:1975
translate schinese chapter13_72cb7484:

    # "Like the previous buildings in town, there are no windows to be seen.{w} What’s most concerning to me is that the front door is nowhere in sight."
    "和之前镇上的建筑一样，窗户没能幸存。{w}不过最令我担心的是从我这里压根看不到家里的前门在哪。"

# game/b13.rpy:1976
translate schinese chapter13_c2bdc9ae:

    # "That feeling of uneasiness washes over me again."
    "不安的感觉涌上心头。"

# game/b13.rpy:1977
translate schinese chapter13_53ebfbe8:

    # "The fact that my home has been violated like this, for who knows how long, isn’t a comforting thought."
    "可以肯定的是我的家早已被洗劫，也不知这事过去多久了，总之这并不让人宽心。"

# game/b13.rpy:1978
translate schinese chapter13_5741b74c:

    # "I don’t even think about looking for the time capsule.{w} I just want to see the damage that’s been done."
    "我甚至不再去想寻找时间胶囊的事。{w}一心只想看看家中的受损程度。"

# game/b13.rpy:1991
translate schinese chapter13_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/b13.rpy:1992
translate schinese chapter13_4417b0e4:

    # "There’s trash littered about, and glass from the windows all over the floor."
    "屋内垃圾四处，地板上布满了玻璃残片。"

# game/b13.rpy:1993
translate schinese chapter13_861f3033:

    # "The only furniture left in the living room has either been torn to shreds or flipped over."
    "客厅里还留下的家具要么被撕成碎片，要么被翻倒过来。"

# game/b13.rpy:1994
translate schinese chapter13_317878ba:

    # "All I can hope for is that the scuffle didn’t include my parents."
    "我现在只能祈祷当时我的父母没被卷入其中。"

# game/b13.rpy:1995
translate schinese chapter13_837618aa:

    # "Their room is the next I make my way into."
    "接下来我要去的地方便是他们的房间。"

# game/b13.rpy:2004
translate schinese chapter13_e72701fe:

    # "The door was clearly kicked in."
    "显然有人破门而入。"

# game/b13.rpy:2005
translate schinese chapter13_738153da:

    # "I hesitate to explore inside, not wanting to accidentally stumble upon their corpses."
    "我犹豫着要不要进去，但我害怕这么做会不小心碰到他们的尸体。"

# game/b13.rpy:2006
translate schinese chapter13_493000a6:

    # "Eventually, curiosity gets the better of me."
    "最终，好奇心战胜了恐惧。"

# game/b13.rpy:2012
translate schinese chapter13_6dc89c43:

    # "I let out a shuddered breath of relief. There’s no one inside."
    "我松了一口气，这里面没人。"

# game/b13.rpy:2013
translate schinese chapter13_877f81b2:

    # "Everything in here is so dusty.{w} I know my mom would throw a fit if she was here."
    "里面的一切布满了尘土。{w}我知道要是我妈看到这里变成这样，肯定会大发雷霆的。"

# game/b13.rpy:2014
translate schinese chapter13_eee11773:

    # "All the drawers are open. I doubt there’s anything sentimental left behind."
    "所有抽屉都已被翻了个遍，我怀疑这还能剩下些什么让我感伤的东西。"

# game/b13.rpy:2016
translate schinese chapter13_a18ac994:

    # "When I turn to make my way out, I see Aaron standing in the doorframe."
    "当我转身走出去时，我看到Aaron正站在门口。"

# game/b13.rpy:2017
translate schinese chapter13_f8da2569:

    # "He’s staring at me with a worried look."
    "他满心忧虑地望着我。"

# game/b13.rpy:2019
translate schinese chapter13_a809205c:

    # "I give him a shrug to try to put him at ease. I’m not really in the mood to talk."
    "我耸了耸肩，试图让他放松，现在的我真的没有心情说话。"

# game/b13.rpy:2029
translate schinese chapter13_af177b1d:

    # "The kitchen is definitely in the worst shape."
    "厨房绝对是被破坏得最严重的地方。"

# game/b13.rpy:2030
translate schinese chapter13_ee18c2c6:

    # "That makes sense, I guess.{w} People looking for food would naturally ransack the kitchen."
    "我想这也说的通。{w}毕竟那些寻找食物的人自然会好好洗劫一番厨房。"

# game/b13.rpy:2031
translate schinese chapter13_d09473a0:

    # "Even the fridge is gone. Dunno what they’d do with it, though."
    "甚至连冰箱都不见了，也不知道偷它的那些人会拿它来做些什么。"

# game/b13.rpy:2032
translate schinese chapter13_fadfcd5c:

    # "Nothing’s in the cupboards anymore.{w} I can still picture the sugary cereal Dad used to get for us when Mom was on business trips."
    "橱柜里什么都没有了。{w}但我仍然可以回想起妈妈每次出差时爸爸为我们买的含糖麦片。"

# game/b13.rpy:2034
translate schinese chapter13_de8a5442:

    # "Heading out of the kitchen, my muscle memory kicks in and I try to turn the non-existent lights off."
    "走出厨房，我的肌肉记忆催使着我试图关掉那盏早已不存在的灯。"

# game/b13.rpy:2035
translate schinese chapter13_eb36a708:

    # "I shake my head and chuckle to myself before walking down the hall to my room."
    "对此我无奈地摇起了头苦笑了一会儿，然后便沿着大厅走到了我的房间。"

# game/b13.rpy:2045
translate schinese chapter13_4e60e852:

    # "Compared to the rest of the house, it’s not nearly as damaged.{w} There’s stuff all over the place and my bed is completely overturned, but it’s still recognizable."
    "与房子的其余部分相比，它并没有受到太多损害。房间里东西散落得到处都是，我的床也被完全掀翻，但起码仍可辨识。"

# game/b13.rpy:2046
translate schinese chapter13_a04e4cd1:

    # "I guess I didn’t have much stuff to take after I moved out."
    "我想我搬出去后也没有什么东西可以带走了。"

# game/b13.rpy:2047
translate schinese chapter13_f7711904:

    # "As if it was my fault, I try to turn the bed over."
    "就好似这是我犯的错，我试图把床翻正过来挽回。"

# game/b13.rpy:2048
translate schinese chapter13_4db88d5a:

    # "After considerable straining, it suddenly moves easily."
    "在我不懈的努力之下，翻床突然变得容易。"

# game/b13.rpy:2050
translate schinese chapter13_2d9a93eb:

    # "Aaron lifts it up effortlessly, placing it against the wall."
    "Aaron很轻松地将它举起，然后把它靠在了墙上。"

# game/b13.rpy:2052
translate schinese chapter13_21469f4e:

    # Aa "How’s that?"
    Aa "这样如何？"

# game/b13.rpy:2053
translate schinese chapter13_e96e0d3d:

    # "I nod before going to sit on it."
    "我点点头，然后去坐了上去。"

# game/b13.rpy:2055
translate schinese chapter13_9461bde8:

    # "A three-century-old mattress is not as comfortable as I thought it would be."
    "这样一张有三百年悠久历史的床垫并没有像我想象中的那么舒适。"

# game/b13.rpy:2056
translate schinese chapter13_fbb83970:

    # "Looking around at my decaying room, it still feels just a little bit like home."
    "环顾着我这破旧的房间，我仍感到一丝家的味道。"

# game/b13.rpy:2057
translate schinese chapter13_26881361:

    # cyr "Here. Wanna sit?"
    cyr "这里，想坐吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:2059
translate schinese chapter13_53fb5de8:

    # Aa "I appreciate the offer, but I’m not sure it’ll survive with me on it."
    Aa "感谢你的邀请，但我不确定它是否能经得住我的体重。"

# game/b13.rpy:2060
translate schinese chapter13_83e7271b:

    # "He instead opts to sit down on the ground and lean back against the bed."
    "他最后选择席地而坐，背靠着床。"

# game/b13.rpy:2062
translate schinese chapter13_2c04e359:

    # Aa "I promise I’m not trying to bug you by repeating this, but are you okay?"
    Aa "我保证不是想要啰嗦重复烦你什么的，但我还是想说，你还好吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:2063
translate schinese chapter13_b462c07f:

    # cyr "I.{cps=3}..{/cps}{w=0.4} I don’t really know, honestly."
    cyr "我.{cps=3}..{/cps}{w=0.4}老实说，我也不知道。"

# game/b13.rpy:2064
translate schinese chapter13_434f3794:

    # "I glance around my room again.{w} God only knows what’s taken place since I’ve been gone."
    "我又环顾了一下我的房间，{w}天知道自从我离开后这里发生了什么。"

# game/b13.rpy:2065
translate schinese chapter13_08a53d54:

    # cyr "Part of me knows it’s home, but after everything that’s happened it’s so foreign to me.{w} It’s like I remember everything, but the land itself has left me behind."
    cyr "我知道这里是家，但是经历了一切之后，这里变得如此陌生。{w}就好比，尽管我记得这一切，但故土却早已把我抛在了它的身后。"

# game/b13.rpy:2067
translate schinese chapter13_e3d26229:

    # Aa "It has been a long time, hasn’t it? I wouldn’t be surprised if it’s been over two hundred years since anyone’s poked their head around here."
    Aa "毕竟这已经过去很久了，不是吗？要是两百年未曾有人来过这里我也不奇怪。"

# game/b13.rpy:2068
translate schinese chapter13_fdcf1eba:

    # Aa "From our records, most people flocked together to survive.{w} Lone stragglers didn’t make it very far."
    Aa "根据我们的记录，大多数人都选择了抱团生存，{w}孤独的流浪者往往活不下去。"

# game/b13.rpy:2069
translate schinese chapter13_168421fc:

    # cyr "Nothing wrong with that. Everything people did to survive makes sense."
    cyr "这没什么错，人们为了生存所做的一切都是合情合理的。"

# game/b13.rpy:2070
translate schinese chapter13_a5d5929f:

    # cyr "Even if it meant breaking into unsuspecting houses for supplies. I can’t blame them."
    cyr "即使这意味着他们要闯入一个毫不设防的房屋以获取补给，我想我也不能责怪他们。"

# game/b13.rpy:2071
translate schinese chapter13_c1b9f64e:

    # "I instinctively lean back on my bed.{w} It’s very stiff and terribly uncomfortable."
    "我本能地向后靠在床上，{w}它的触感十分僵硬令人不适。"

# game/b13.rpy:2072
translate schinese chapter13_6a182857:

    # cyr "Still... I was hoping I’d be able to bring stuff back with me."
    cyr "但...我还是希望我能拿回那些属于我的东西。"

# game/b13.rpy:2074
translate schinese chapter13_e54a8138:

    # Aa "Well, we still have the time capsule to dig up."
    Aa "好吧，我们还有时间胶囊可挖。"

# game/b13.rpy:2075
translate schinese chapter13_87eb6d22:

    # cyr "Oh, duh! The thing we came here for."
    cyr "哦，对哦！我差点忘了我们来这里是为了这事。"

# game/b13.rpy:2077
translate schinese chapter13_13b8227f:

    # Aa "Do you remember where you buried it?"
    Aa "你还记得你把它埋在哪里了吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:2078
translate schinese chapter13_21ef8d91:

    # cyr "I think I have a good idea."
    cyr "我想我记得。"

# game/b13.rpy:2090
translate schinese chapter13_25a6db24:

    # "I’m happy to see that the backyard was left relatively unscathed."
    "我很高兴看到家里后院相对来说毫发无损。"

# game/b13.rpy:2091
translate schinese chapter13_3b8f2330:

    # "There’s some toppled furniture and long dead plants, but it’s pretty similar to what I remember it as."
    "这有一些倒塌的家具以及一些枯枝败叶，但它们的位置与我记忆中的情况出入不大。"

# game/b13.rpy:2092
translate schinese chapter13_dd0674b6:

    # "I remember helping Mom set up her new patio. She said a metal table and chairs would last longer."
    "我记得过去我帮助妈妈装饰她的新庭院的时候，她有提到过一张金属桌椅能用很长一段时间。"

# game/b13.rpy:2093
translate schinese chapter13_fa5b39ce:

    # "Guess she wasn’t wrong."
    "她说得一点儿也没有错。"

# game/b13.rpy:2094
translate schinese chapter13_690f9abe:

    # "The vegetation is overgrown, like the rest of the town. Sadly, the big tree we had must have died a long time ago."
    "这里杂草丛生，就像镇上的其他地方一样。可惜的是，我们的那棵大树在很久以前就死去了。"

# game/b13.rpy:2095
translate schinese chapter13_c374fa75:

    # "Now it’s just a big husk."
    "现在它只是一个巨大的干树壳。"

# game/b13.rpy:2096
translate schinese chapter13_cf6c3fea:

    # "Sliding my fingers against the dry bark confirms that fact to me."
    "我的手指在干燥的树皮上滑动，树皮的触感进一步证明了我的想法。"

# game/b13.rpy:2097
translate schinese chapter13_f74eccac:

    # cyr "Man... I remember climbing this thing when I was little."
    cyr "天...我记得我小时候还爬过这颗树呢。"

# game/b13.rpy:2098
translate schinese chapter13_8ee5c5df:

    # "Mom would give me a piggyback ride to help me all the way to the top, mainly because Dad was too scared."
    "妈妈会给我一个肩驮帮助我一路爬到树顶，不过这么做主要还是因为爸爸太害怕放心不下我。"

# game/b13.rpy:2099
translate schinese chapter13_d140f3c1:

    # "Now it looks like a sneeze could knock it over."
    "但就现在这个状态，似乎稍稍打个喷嚏都可以把树打翻。"

# game/b13.rpy:2100
translate schinese chapter13_a5b9ee4e:

    # "I shake my head. I’m getting distracted again."
    "我摇摇头，我又分心了。"

# game/b13.rpy:2101
translate schinese chapter13_5ebbd8c3:

    # "My gaze falls to the ground at the base of the tree."
    "我将目光转向树根。"

# game/b13.rpy:2102
translate schinese chapter13_0e369d72:

    # cyr "It should be down here. Do you have a shovel?"
    cyr "胶囊应该在这里，你有带铲子吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:2104
translate schinese chapter13_8f13cfb0:

    # Aa "On it."
    Aa "马上来。"

# game/b13.rpy:2106
translate schinese chapter13_a5c782f8:

    # "Aaron takes out his Axiom inventory screen to materialize a shiny shovel."
    "Aaron打开了他Axiom的物品栏，将一把闪亮的铲子具现化了出来。"

# game/b13.rpy:2107
translate schinese chapter13_db33a0a5:

    # cyr "You gotta remind me to stock mine with useful things like that."
    cyr "你这倒是提醒了我应该在我的Axiom里放些有用的东西。"

# game/b13.rpy:2109
translate schinese chapter13_62eca519:

    # Aa "It is quite handy. Do you want me to dig?"
    Aa "挺方便的，你想让我帮你挖吗？"

# game/b13.rpy:2110
translate schinese chapter13_a8f42942:

    # cyr "I’d like to try for a little while, if that’s alright."
    cyr "我想如果可以的话，我还是先自己挖吧。"

# game/b13.rpy:2112
translate schinese chapter13_b037d8b6:

    # Aa "Of course. Here. Just be careful."
    Aa "当然，拿好，小心别伤到就好。"

 # game/b13.rpy:2113
translate schinese chapter13_176b1281:

    # "I nod and take the shovel, feeling its weight in my hands.{w} It’s heavy enough where I’m definitely going to need both hands to get anywere."
    "我点点头，拿起铁锹，掂量着它在我手中的分量。{w}它确实有够重的，我肯定需要两只手才能拿得起它。"

# game/b13.rpy:2114
translate schinese chapter13_d6a03977:

    # cyr "I’ve never actually done this before.{w} The time capsule should be sturdy, but let’s hope I don’t break it."
    cyr "我从未做过这样的事。{w}时间胶囊应该相当坚固，但我还是希望不要一不小心挖坏了它。"

# game/b13.rpy:2116
translate schinese chapter13_ff7f9d8b:

    # Aa "Just take it easy. We’re on vacation, after all."
    Aa "慢慢来就好，我们可是正在度假呢。"

# game/b13.rpy:2117
translate schinese chapter13_e96a9930:

    # cyr "A well deserved one, at that."
    cyr "是啊，而且还是意义非凡的一次。"

# game/b13.rpy:2120
translate schinese chapter13_0efe8f00:

    # "I take a deep breath and then pierce the ground with force, ready to get started."
    "我深吸一口气，随后用力将铁锹扎入地面，开始挖了起来。"

# game/b13.rpy:2138
translate schinese chapter13_973caa2d:
#*鱼/炽镜-来自过去的信
    # "While not erratic, my heavy breathing breaks the silence we’ve found ourselves in."
    "铁锹一下一下的挥动，我的呼吸也变得粗重，但不失平稳，打破了这一方院落的寂静。"

# game/b13.rpy:2139
translate schinese chapter13_9add9512:

    # "It’s only been 10 minutes and I’m already exhausted.{w} Just how far did we bury it...?"
    "才过10分钟我就已经精疲力尽了。{w}我们那时到底把它埋在哪儿了..."

# game/b13.rpy:2141
translate schinese chapter13_a20cefa7_1:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/b13.rpy:2142
translate schinese chapter13_a1474a05:

    # "I hear the shovel clink against something metallic and out of place."
    "我听见铲子发出了一声金属的闷响。"

# game/b13.rpy:2143
translate schinese chapter13_e542544e:

    # "The fruits of my labor are starting to show themselves.{w} With an excited smile, I plant the shovel down into the dirt and get on my knees."
    "劳动的甘果马上就要成熟了。{w}我面露笑色，接着把铲子插进土里，蹲了下去。"

# game/b13.rpy:2147
translate schinese chapter13_9ab8db86:

    # "I frantically push away the surrounding dirt with my hands."
    "然后焦急地翻开了周围的泥土。"

# game/b13.rpy:2148
translate schinese chapter13_1f64b401:

    # "Eventually, I manage to dig out the centuries-old time capsule."
    "最后，我找到了这被尘封几世纪之久的时间胶囊。"

# game/b13.rpy:2149
translate schinese chapter13_f1050031:

    # "I know it was meant to last a long time, but it’s definitely showing its age."
    "它的外观时刻向我倾吐着它的年岁。"

# game/b13.rpy:2151
translate schinese chapter13_0a1add73:

    # Aa "Oh!{w=0.3} You found it!"
    Aa "噢！{w=0.3}你挖到了！"

# game/b13.rpy:2152
translate schinese chapter13_481944c8:

    # "Aaron gets up from the patio furniture and then comes to inspect it with me."
    "Aaron从户外家具之间来到了我这里，和我一起打量起了它。"

# game/b13.rpy:2153
translate schinese chapter13_80515d28:

    # "It’s no bigger than a shoebox. A rusty, rusty shoebox."
    "它不如一个鞋盒大，鞋盒还得是那种锈得不能再锈的铁鞋盒。"

# game/b13.rpy:2155
translate schinese chapter13_9b1776be:

    # cyr "Wow..."
    cyr "哇噢..."

# game/b13.rpy:2156
translate schinese chapter13_5111f6be:

    # "A part of me doesn’t want to open it, just in case the contents didn’t survive all this time."
    "我有点儿不想打开它，毕竟担心里面的东西没能保存下来。"

# game/b13.rpy:2157
translate schinese chapter13_4ecc4af3:

    # "I look back at the house and then stand up, deciding to open it at the table."
    "回望这座房子之后，我还是决定在桌子上将它打开。"

# game/b13.rpy:2159
translate schinese chapter13_55a1a2b0:

    # Aa "Hm?"
    Aa "嗯？"

# game/b13.rpy:2161
translate schinese chapter13_7ae23372:

    # "I don’t notice Aaron staying behind."
    "我没有注意到身后的Aaron。"

# game/b13.rpy:2162
translate schinese chapter13_b41e70a0:

    # "I’m enamored by the capsule.{w} It’s weird to think that something concrete from my past has survived for this long."
    "我被这个盒子深深迷住了。{w}想到那时的物什就在这盒子里，我不禁觉得奇妙。"

# game/b13.rpy:2163
translate schinese chapter13_bf6f0c29:

    # "I keep staring at it after putting it on the table.{w} Eventually, I place my hand on one of the locks."
