# game/b13.rpy:2693
translate schinese chapter13_519f8614:

    # "Without any curtains, what little sunlight is out peaks through the window."
    "没有任何窗帘，阳光在房里肆无忌惮。"

# game/b13.rpy:2695
translate schinese chapter13_e56291a5:

    # "Even though it’s still early, it’s enough to wake me up."
    "尽管时间还很早，但我还是想起来。"

# game/b13.rpy:2696
translate schinese chapter13_c51e5d11:

    # "Thankfully, I’m not as tired as I thought I would be.{w} I guess I did tucker myself out last night."
    "幸好，我并不像我想象的那样累。{w}我昨晚也许真的有把自己弄得疲惫不堪吧。"

# game/b13.rpy:2697
translate schinese chapter13_5e85914c:

    # "Something does feel strange, though.{w} What am I sleeping on?"
    "不过，有件事确实感觉很怪——我睡在什么上面？"

# game/b13.rpy:2699
translate schinese chapter13_97a83ceb:

    # "It’s not a pillow.{w} It’s warm and fluffy and-"
    "不像是个枕头。它又温暖，又蓬松，而且还——"

# game/b13.rpy:2706
translate schinese chapter13_2b619b90:

    # "I crack my eyes open to see Aaron right in front of me."
    "我揉揉眼睛，看到Aaron就出现在我面前。"

# game/b13.rpy:2707
translate schinese chapter13_05eadc69:

    # "He must have brought me in close while we were sleeping, I’m practically being hugged against him."
    "他睡觉时肯定把我搂得很近，我也的确是被他抱在怀里。"

# game/b13.rpy:2708
translate schinese chapter13_7b80644c:

    # "My hand is resting on his exposed stomach, pressing into his soft fur."
    "我把手放在他裸露的肚子上，rua了rua他柔软的毛发。"

# game/b13.rpy:2709
translate schinese chapter13_52d101a6:

    # "I just stare at him for a while as he snores."
    "他呼噜起来，我盯着他看了一会儿。"

# game/b13.rpy:2710
translate schinese chapter13_f1f957fd:

    # "There’s a slight chill in the air.{w} The house is pretty drafty, and there’s no power for the heat anymore, so it probably got cold last night."
    "空气中有一丝寒意。{w}这所房子非常通风，而且已经没有电暖气了，所以昨晚可能很冷。"

# game/b13.rpy:2711
translate schinese chapter13_fcd6a0e0:

    # "That’s just like Aaron, worrying about me while we sleep."
    "确实是Aaron会做的事，在睡觉时还担心着我。"

# game/b13.rpy:2712
translate schinese chapter13_9ef6156a:

    # "I give the paw resting on his chest a small squeeze, I don’t want to wake him up."
    "我轻轻捏了捏放在他胸前的爪子，不想把他吵醒。"

# game/b13.rpy:2713
translate schinese chapter13_86fc9773:

    # "That dream is fresh in my mind."
    "那个梦我还记忆犹新。"

# game/b13.rpy:2714
translate schinese chapter13_4f9398db:

    # "Out of all the memories I repressed, I can’t believe that one stayed dormant as long as it did."
    "不敢相信，除了那些被我遏抑的过往外，我还保存了这般栩栩如生的回忆。"
