# game/b13.rpy:2715
translate schinese chapter13_b8b6c3ad:

    # "I rub Aaron’s chest as he sleeps, like I used to do with Damion."
    "Aaron仍旧徜徉在自己的梦乡，我揉着他的胸口，就像我以前对Damion那样。"

# game/b13.rpy:2716
translate schinese chapter13_9bbc30a2:

    # "Not only because it’d make him happy, but because it made me happy too."
    "这能让他高兴，更能让我高兴。"

# game/b13.rpy:2717
translate schinese chapter13_8df147ac:

    # "He starts to purr. The rumbling moves through his throat and chest."
    "咕噜声在他的喉咙和胸腔中隆隆作响。"

# game/b13.rpy:2718
translate schinese chapter13_854e04c7:

    # "It makes me smile."
    "我笑了起来。"

# game/b13.rpy:2719
translate schinese chapter13_47c89a13:

    # "Feeling determined, I slowly try to make myself out of the tigers grasp."
    "我清醒了大半，慢慢脱离白虎的怀抱。"

# game/b13.rpy:2720
translate schinese chapter13_22763f35:

    # "I’m only wearing my sweatpants, but that should be enough for a small walk. I'm used to this weather."
    "我只穿着卫裤，但这对我来说应该足够了，我已经习惯了这种天气。"

# game/b13.rpy:2721
translate schinese chapter13_6a84f755:

    # "I have a lot to think about."
    "我有很多事情还要思考。"

# game/b13.rpy:2727
translate schinese chapter13_bc5d95de:

    # "Sure enough, the sun is still inching over the horizon."
    "正如所料，太阳仍腻在地平线上，不愿起身。"

# game/b13.rpy:2728
translate schinese chapter13_2d46994f:

    # "I’ve watched the sun rise more in the past couple months than I did living in the past."
    "过去两个月里，我目睹太阳升起的次数远超了以往300年的总和。"

# game/b13.rpy:2729
translate schinese chapter13_7f63bb93:

    # "It feels warmer than usual.{w} I smile and look around."
    "感觉这次比平常更加暖和。{w}我笑着环顾四周。"

# game/b13.rpy:2730
translate schinese chapter13_56ca37de:

    # "I look back at my abandoned house.{w} I should be able to take a quick walk without being noticed, right?"
    "我回头看了看我那已被抛弃的房子。{w}我再走几圈，应该不会被发现吧？"

# game/b13.rpy:2741
translate schinese chapter13_86cf62b5:

    # "My walk takes me through my hometown.{w} Unlike yesterday, that nagging feel of dread has all but washed away."
    "我漫步走过我的故乡。{w}与昨天不同的是，那种沮丧缠身的感觉已经所剩无几了。"

# game/b13.rpy:2742
translate schinese chapter13_a9f7be01:

    # "Sure, it’s a little depressing to see everything like this."
    "当然，看到这样的一切还是有点令人失落的。"

# game/b13.rpy:2743
translate schinese chapter13_6f9a78f6:

    # "But I feel too good to let that stop me from enjoying myself."
    "但我不能让它坏了我的心情。"

# game/b13.rpy:2744
translate schinese chapter13_b4ff04b3:

    # "Now more than ever I feel like I have a purpose."
    "此时此刻，有种决心在我的心里萌芽——"

# game/b13.rpy:2745
translate schinese chapter13_c3a207d9:

    # "I want to help take down Current- no, Resoom."
