translate schinese chapter13_06c393fe:

    # "I want people like Vita to feel safe enough to walk around without fear of being kidnapped and experimented on."
    "我希望，那些像Vita这样的人，也能放下再被抓去做实验的担忧，安心地四处走走。"

# game/b13.rpy:2751
translate schinese chapter13_fce5c863:

    # "Despite what Silver might say, I think he deserves more in life than just being an assassin.{w} I hope I can help him and Ash find a stable life."
    "不论Silver会怎么说，我都认为他值得过上更好的生活，而非仅作为一个刺客。{w}我希望，我能帮助他和Ash找到一种稳定的生活。"

# game/b13.rpy:2752
translate schinese chapter13_7b8fcaa5:

    # "Karin looks like she wants to have a good time, she’d make for an excellent motivational speaker.{w} She seems to be the most content with how things are currently."
