# game/b13.rpy:2754
translate schinese chapter13_bb6a9aeb:

    # "While Canto can be a prick, I can tell he has good intentions. He genuinely wants Silver to be happy.{w} They’ve been going through some friction as of late, I’d like to be able to help them work it out if possible."
    "虽然Canto可能是个刺头，但我其实可以看出他怀揣的善意。他是真心希望Silver幸福的。{w}他们最近有一些摩擦。如果可以，我希望能够帮助他们解决这个问题。"

# game/b13.rpy:2759
translate schinese chapter13_55cd49f9:

    # "More and more memories of my friends cycle through my mind.{w} The dinners we’ve had together, the long talks in the middle of therapy, these people are very precious to me."
    "那些和朋友在一起的回忆在我脑海中不断涌现——{w}我们一起吃过的晚餐，在治疗过程中的长谈，还有那一段段弥足珍贵的友谊。"

# game/b13.rpy:2760
translate schinese chapter13_b7e9905c:

    # "Especially Aaron. Out of everyone, he’s definitely hurting the most.{w} Even if he doesn’t end up reciprocating my feelings toward him, I want to make sure I’m there to help him heal."
    "特别是Aaron。在所有人中，他肯定是受伤最深的。{w}即使他最终没有回应我对他的感情，我也想要一直陪伴他，疗愈他。"

# game/b13.rpy:2761
translate schinese chapter13_f6e65808:

    # "And, most of all, I want to get to the bottom of what happened to Xavier.{w} Who knows what they’re doing to him, if he’s still alive."
    "而且，最重要的是，我想弄清楚发生在Xavier身上的事。{w}谁知道他们在对他做着些什么，如果他还活着的话。"

# game/b13.rpy:2762
translate schinese chapter13_920e2722:

    # "I know full well what they’re capable of.{w} I don’t want Aaron to find that out first hand."
    "我清楚地知道他们能做什么。{w}我不想让Aaron这么快察觉到这一点。"

# game/b13.rpy:2763
translate schinese chapter13_2b2f8ec2:

    # "He’s been protecting me since we met, the least I can do is try to return the favor."
    "自我们相识以来，他就一直在保护我，我至少也应该做些什么，来努力回报他的帮助。"

